quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,( yeh ) log kis cheez ki nisbat puchhte hain ?
  78,2,(kiya ) barri khabar ki nisbat ?
  78,3,jis mein yeh ikhtilaaf kar rahay hain
  78,4,dekho yeh anqareeb jaan len ge
  78,5,phir dekho yeh anqareeb jaan len ge
  78,6,kiya hum ne zameen ko bichona nahi banaya
  78,7,aur pahoron ko ( a seen ki ) maikhain ( nahi thehraya? )
  78,8,( be shak banaya ) aur tum ko jora jora bhi pedakiya
  78,9,aur neend ko tumahray liye ( mojab ) aaraam banaya
  78,10,aur raat ko parda muqarrarkiya
  78,11,aur din ko muaash ( ka waqt ) qarar diya
  78,12,aur tumahray oopar saat mazboot ( aasman ) banaye
  78,13,aur ( aftaab ka ) roshan chairag banaya
  78,14,aur nichartay baadalon se mosla dhaar meen barsaya
  78,15,taakay is se anaaj aur sabza peda karen
  78,16,aur ghany ghany baagh
  78,17,be shak faisla ka din muqarrar hai
  78,18,jis din sor phonka jaye ga to tum log ghat ke ghat aa mojood ho ge
  78,19,aur aasman khoola jaye ga to ( is mein ) darwazay ho jayen ge
  78,20,aur pahar chalaye jayen ge to woh rait ho kar reh jayen ge
  78,21,be shak dozakh ghaat mein hai
  78,22,( yani ) sarkashon ka wohi thikana hai
  78,23,is mein woh muddaton parre rahen ge
  78,24,wahan nah thandak ka maza chakhain ge. nah ( kuch ) piinaa ( naseeb ho ga )
  78,25,magar garam pani aur behti peep
  78,26,( yeh ) badla hai poora poora
  78,27,yeh log hisaab ( akhirat ) ki umeed hi nahi rakhtay they
  78,28,aur hamari ayaton ko jhoot samajh kar jutlatay rehtay they
  78,29,aur hum ne har cheez ko likh kar zabt kar rakha hai
  78,30,so ( ab ) maza chako. hum tum par azaab hi berhate jayen ge
